{"tid":888322,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你是你，我是我。","createTime":"2018-11-03T15:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T15:52:03.000Z","uid":11403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fc427b0c0082d12d03a47c51ad315bcc62c5bafb","tid":888322,"uid":11403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T15:50:31.000Z","msg":"我做我的事，你做你的事。<br />\n我並不是為了滿足你的期望而存在這個世界。<br />\n你並不是為了滿足我的期望而活在這個地方。<br />\n你是你，我是我。<br />\n如果偶然間能夠彼此相遇，那是件很美好的事。<br />\n如果無法相遇，那也無可奈何。"},{"pid":"f1a61367785b3cd6e21821ae4d4fcf05dc8cee7c","tid":888322,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T15:52:03.000Z","msg":"冇女"}]}